data.description: Well maintained one owner home in great location. Open floor plan, Custom features, trey ceiling in owners suite, extensive trim, larger walk in shower with grab bar. Enclosed 3 season room, 19.8 x13 glass windows and screens.  Wide doors, space saving pocket doors, powder room, storm shelter in garage. Microwave 2 yrs old HVAC compressor 2.5 yrs. old compacitor & return air fan 1 yr old.
